{"tid":1467346,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要做好公關呀","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:11.000Z","uid":101315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c70a7fb92362c9d5dea33f00196ca8577ab97b","tid":1467346,"uid":101315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"不合作運動，無疑係要用經濟損失令政府屈服。<br />\n<br />\n但有兩樣野要留意：<br />\n1）不合作運動，一定要多人參與至有用。你要說服民眾加入不合作的行列呀。<br />\n2）而不合作運動帶來的損失，會影響到所有人，政府可以會甘啲，但點搞都唔會係 surgically clear 架。<br />\n<br />\n即是說，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你要說服一群受到損失我人加入我地</span></span></strong>。不論抗爭現場有幾多人，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">人永遠是不夠的</span></span></span></strong>。你不爭取更多人加入抗爭，摺得。<br />\n<br />\n這就是不合作運動無可避免的兩難。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">力度唔夠，政府唔驚；力度太大，易得罪民眾，會愈做愈縮。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n結論係：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動，抗爭力度愈大、宣傳力度也要愈大。</span></strong></span>抗爭和宣傳拍住上，抗爭才會搞得大，才會有效果。<br />\n<br />\n不要說不須討好民眾：讓他們同情抗爭、使他們考慮加入我們，是大家的責任。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，當然不能割蓆。但單單不割蓆是不夠的。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">在場外的，要想想如何為前線辯護；在前線的，也要想想如何不要令辯護者難做。</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e55b3ed501a0e5679c45db81307599c64ad3d91","tid":1467346,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"}]}